; 2. What are semantic tags and why are they important in HTML5?

; âœ… Answer:
; Semantic tags give meaning to the structure of a webpage.
; Examples: <header>, <nav>, <section>, <article>, <footer>.
; 	â€¢	They improve SEO (search engines understand content better).
; 	â€¢	They improve Accessibility (A11Y) for screen readers.
; 	â€¢	They make the DOM easier for developers to maintain.
