  <header><h2>Blog Title</h2></header>
  <p>Post content...</p>
  <footer>Author: Srikanth</footer>
</article>


3. Difference between async and defer in HTML5 <script> tag?

âœ… Answer:
	â€¢	async â†’ Script loads independently and executes immediately (can block DOM). Best for analytics/ads.
	â€¢	defer â†’ Script loads in parallel but executes after DOM is parsed. Best for app logic.

ğŸ‘‰ Example:
